Package: OptimizationReg
Title: This package calculates Minimization and Maximization for 
     Linear regression Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Ahmed Samir [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0000-0000-0000>)
Maintainer: Ahmed Samir <samir.megahed@gmail.com>
Description: A specialized tool for estimating regression parameters (Intercept and Slope) 
    using Ordinary Least Squares (OLS) and Maximum Likelihood Estimation (MLE) 
    within educational psychology research.
